title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 03 2013
description:
October 03, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 


Hour One: Is Obamacare the GOP's Waterloo?

Hour Two: Is it un-American or un-Christian to threaten to takeover America by force?  Pastor Rick Joyner, Morning Star Ministries / Plus, Geeky Science - America...all fracked up

Hour Three: Is this the beginning or the end of the Tea Party?  Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio
